===Noun===
'''temperance'''
#[[Habitual]] [[moderation]] in regard to the [[indulgence]] of the [[natural]] [[appetite]]s and [[passions]]; [[restrain]]ed or [[moderate]] indulgence; moderation; as, temperance in eating and drinking; temperance in the indulgence of joy or mirth; specifically, moderation, and sometimes [[abstinence]], in respect to using [[intoxicate|intoxicating]] [[liquor]]s.
#[[Moderation]] of [[passion]]; [[patience]]; [[calmness]]; [[sedateness]].
#State with regard to [[heat]] or [[cold]]; [[temperature]].
